<item>
            <title>[SOLR-10319] SolrCore &quot;instanceDir&quot; metric not visible in JMX</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-10319</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This metric exposes &lt;tt&gt;SolrResourceLoader.getInstancePath()&lt;/tt&gt; as a gauge but &lt;tt&gt;java.nio.Path&lt;/tt&gt; is not one of the &lt;tt&gt;OpenType&lt;/tt&gt; allowed classes, and it shows up as &quot;Unavailable&quot; in JConsole.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The fix is to simply convert it toString.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
